thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Gary

author: Gary
title: Gary
text: I live in an area where I can't get fresh seafood locally. Even though Maine Lobster Now is all the way across the country their product was of interest, so I ordered fresh lobster meat and fresh fish. The products were delivered on time, in perfect condition, and were of excellent quality.
